# ai-engineering-harness

This project uses the ai-engineering-harness capability pack.

Before implementation:

1. Read `.harness/HARNESS.md`, `TEAM.md`, `SKILLS.md`, `WORKFLOW.md`, `GATES.md`, and active goal artifacts under `.harness/goals/` when they exist.
2. Do not invent requirements or architecture; read artifacts first.
3. Follow the harness command loop: map → start → discuss → plan → run → verify → ship → remember.
4. Prefer surgical changes; verify before claiming done.
5. Never store secrets or private data in `.harness/` files.

If `.harness/` is missing, ask the user to run: `install.sh --runtime cursor --scope project --init-harness`
